# Design System Rules

Follow these rules when generating or modifying HTML/CSS for this portfolio.

## Core Principles

- **Less is more** — fewer variations, more consistency
- **Flat and white** — no shadows, no gradients
- **Dark text** — gray-800 for all text (not gray-600)
- **Ample spacing** — generous gaps, especially around text
- **Light borders** — border-gray-200 only
- **Consistent radius** — rounded-xl for containers, rounded-full for pills

## Typography

### Font Weights (use only these 3)

- `font-bold` (700) — headings, emphasis
- `font-medium` (500) — navigation, UI labels
- Default (400) — body text

**Do NOT use:** `font-semibold`, `font-light`, `font-thin`, `font-black`

### Text Colors

- `text-gray-800` — default for ALL text (headings and body)
- `text-gray-500` — muted/secondary (captions, dates only)
- `text-blue-600` — links only

**Do NOT use:** `text-gray-600`, `text-gray-700`, `text-gray-900` for body text

### Headings

Use semantic HTML. CSS handles sizing automatically:
- `<h1>` — 36px bold
- `<h2>` — 24px bold  
- `<h3>` — 20px bold

**Do NOT add** `text-2xl`, `text-3xl`, `font-bold` to headings — they inherit from CSS.

### Body Text Sizes

Two body text sizes available:

- **16px (default):** General body text, multi-column layouts, cards, metadata, UI elements
- **18px (`.text-body-lg`):** Single full-width columns, article/blog content, long-form reading, case study content

**Usage:**
- Default 16px applies automatically to all `<p>` tags
- For larger text in single-column layouts, add `.text-body-lg` class to paragraphs or their container
- Example: `<p class="text-body-lg">Content for single-column reading</p>`

## Colors

### Backgrounds

Only two options:
- `bg-white` — default
- `bg-gray-50` — alternating sections

**Do NOT use:** `bg-gray-100`, `bg-blue-*`, shadows, gradients

### Borders

- Always `border-gray-200`
- Never darker borders

### Accent Color

- `text-blue-600` / `hover:text-blue-800` — for links only
- No blue backgrounds or badges

## Spacing

Use ample gaps:

- Section padding: `py-12 lg:py-16` with `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Heading to content: `mb-6`
- Paragraphs: `space-y-5` or `mt-5`
- Grid gaps: `gap-8 lg:gap-12`
- Tag groups: `gap-2`

## Border Radius

Only two values:
- `rounded-xl` — cards, images, containers
- `rounded-full` — pills, avatars, icon buttons

**Do NOT use:** `rounded-lg`, `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-md`

## Components

**CRITICAL:** Always use documented patterns from `/COMPONENTS.md`. Do not create variations.

### Preline UI Components

Use these exact patterns (see COMPONENTS.md for full details):

- **Header with collapse:** `hs-collapse-toggle` with `data-hs-collapse` attribute
- **Dropdown menu:** `hs-dropdown`, `hs-dropdown-toggle`, `hs-dropdown-menu` with required attributes

### Standard Patterns

Use these exact class strings:

**Tag:**
```html
<span class="py-1.5 px-3 bg-white text-gray-800 border border-gray-200 text-sm rounded-xl">Label</span>
```

**Project Card:**
```html
<a class="group flex flex-col focus:outline-hidden" href="...">
  <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <img class="max-w-full max-h-full group-hover:scale-105 group-focus:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out object-contain rounded-2xl" src="..." alt="...">
  </div>
  <div class="pt-4">
    <h3>Title</h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">Description</p>
    <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><!-- Tags --></div>
  </div>
</a>
```

**Social Icon Button:**
```html
<a class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50" href="..." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
  <i class="ph ph-linkedin-logo size-4"></i>
</a>
```

**Link with Arrow:**
```html
<a class="group inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-800 hover:text-blue-600 focus:outline-none focus:text-blue-600" href="...">
  <i class="ph ph-arrow-left size-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition"></i>
  Link text
</a>
```

**Section Container:**
```html
<div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16 mx-auto">
```

**Figure with Caption:**
```html
<figure class="my-8">
  <img class="w-full object-cover rounded-xl" src="..." alt="...">
  <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-gray-500">Caption</figcaption>
</figure>
```

## Icons

Use Phosphor Icons with `size-4`:

```html
<i class="ph ph-icon-name size-4"></i>
```

## What NOT to Do

- ❌ No shadows (`shadow-*`)
- ❌ No `font-semibold` — use `font-bold` or `font-medium`
- ❌ No `text-gray-600` — use `text-gray-800`
- ❌ No colored backgrounds
- ❌ No inline heading size overrides
- ❌ No `rounded-lg` or `rounded-2xl` — use `rounded-xl`

